---
title:  Ranch-Spiced Chicken & Corn Rice Bowls with Dark Meat Chicken, Roasted Zucchini & Creamy BBQ
description: For all you dark meat chicken fans in the house: Your day has dawned, and it couldn’t have happened to a nicer bowl! This family-friendly dinner starts with fluffy rice topped with seared ranch-seasoned chicken, corn, and tender roasted zucchini. Finish with a drizzle of tangy, creamy BBQ ranch sauce and serve it all up in a speedy 25 minutes.

